---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NavSimple from '../components/NavSimple.astro';
import '../styles/submit.css';

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<Layout
  title="投稿・信息纠错 | 81日本"
  description="向81日本提交新医院信息、纠正现有错误，或提供其他建议，共同完善在日中文医疗信息库。"
  path="/submit"
  noindex={true}
>
  <NavSimple />

  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">
      <span class="zh-only">投稿</span>
      <span class="en-only">Contribute</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="zh-only">帮我们<em>完善</em>这份指南</h1>
    <h1 class="en-only">Help us <em>improve</em> this guide</h1>
    <p class="zh-only">知道某家提供中文服务的医院还没收录？或者发现信息有误？都欢迎告诉我们。</p>
    <p class="en-only">Know a hospital with Chinese-speaking staff that we haven't listed? Or spotted an error? Let us know.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page-main">
    <aside class="side-info">
      <h3 class="zh-only">投稿流程</h3>
      <h3 class="en-only">How it works</h3>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title zh-only">填写表单</div>
            <div class="step-title en-only">Fill in the form</div>
            <div class="step-desc zh-only">告诉我们医院名称、地址及语言服务等信息</div>
            <div class="step-desc en-only">Tell us the hospital name, location and language services</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title zh-only">人工核实</div>
            <div class="step-title en-only">Manual review</div>
            <div class="step-desc zh-only">我们收到通知后会核实信息的准确性</div>
            <div class="step-desc en-only">We'll verify the information after receiving your submission</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title zh-only">更新上线</div>
            <div class="step-title en-only">Published</div>
            <div class="step-desc zh-only">确认无误后更新到网站，通常1–3天内完成</div>
            <div class="step-desc en-only">Once confirmed, we'll add it to the site within 1–3 days</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="side-note">
        <span class="zh-only">纠错请注明具体问题及信息来源，这样我们能更快处理。</span>
        <span class="en-only">For corrections, please include the specific issue and a source if possible.</span>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div>
      <div class="form-card" id="formCard">
        <div class="type-row">
          <button class="type-btn active" onclick="switchType('new', this)">
            <span class="zh-only">＋ 新增医院</span>
            <span class="en-only">＋ Add hospital</span>
          </button>
          <button class="type-btn" onclick="switchType('fix', this)">
            <span class="zh-only">✎ 纠错/补充</span>
            <span class="en-only">✎ Correction</span>
          </button>
          <button class="type-btn" onclick="switchType('other', this)">
            <span class="zh-only">⊙ 其他建议</span>
            <span class="en-only">⊙ Other</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        <form class="form" id="submitForm" action="/api/submit" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="投稿类型" id="typeHidden" value="新增医院" />
          <input type="text" name="_honey" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute; left:-9999px; opacity:0" />

          <div id="fields-new">
            <div class="form-row">
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">医院名称</span><span class="en-only">Hospital name</span> <span class="req">*</span></label>
                <input class="form-input" type="text" name="医院名称" id="f-name" placeholder="中文或日文均可" />
              </div>
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">所在地</span><span class="en-only">Location</span> <span class="req">*</span></label>
                <input class="form-input" type="text" name="所在地" id="f-location" placeholder="都道府县・城市" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row" style="margin-top:0">
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">语言服务</span><span class="en-only">Language</span> <span class="req">*</span></label>
                <select class="form-input form-select" name="语言服务" id="f-lang">
                  <option value="">请选择…</option>
                  <option value="中文（普通话）">中文（普通话）</option>
                  <option value="中文（广东话）">中文（广东话）</option>
                  <option value="中文＋英文">中文＋英文</option>
                  <option value="英文">英文</option>
                  <option value="其他">其他</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">科室</span><span class="en-only">Department</span></label>
                <input class="form-input" type="text" name="科室" placeholder="内科、産科、歯科…" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row" style="margin-top:0">
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">电话号码</span><span class="en-only">Phone</span></label>
                <input class="form-input" type="text" name="电话" placeholder="03-XXXX-XXXX" />
              </div>
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">官网 / SNS</span><span class="en-only">Website</span></label>
                <input class="form-input" type="text" name="网址" placeholder="https://…" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">营业时间</span><span class="en-only">Hours</span></label>
              <input class="form-input" type="text" name="营业时间"
                placeholder="例：周一至周五 9:00–17:30 / 周六 9:00–12:30" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">备注</span><span class="en-only">Notes</span></label>
              <textarea class="form-input form-textarea" name="备注" id="f-note"
                placeholder="是否需要预约、休息日、注意事项等…"
                oninput="updateChar(this,'c1')"></textarea>
              <div class="char-count" id="c1">0 / 300</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div id="fields-fix" style="display:none">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">哪家医院</span><span class="en-only">Hospital name</span> <span class="req">*</span></label>
              <input class="form-input" type="text" name="纠错-医院名称" id="f-fix-name" placeholder="医院名称" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">问题描述</span><span class="en-only">Describe the issue</span> <span class="req">*</span></label>
              <textarea class="form-input form-textarea" name="纠错-问题描述" id="f-fix-desc"
                placeholder="哪里有误？正确信息是什么？如有来源请附上。"
                style="min-height:110px" oninput="updateChar(this,'c2')"></textarea>
              <div class="char-count" id="c2">0 / 300</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div id="fields-other" style="display:none">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">你的建议</span><span class="en-only">Your suggestion</span> <span class="req">*</span></label>
              <textarea class="form-input form-textarea" name="建议内容" id="f-other"
                placeholder="功能建议、内容补充、合作意向等…"
                style="min-height:110px" oninput="updateChar(this,'c3')"></textarea>
              <div class="char-count" id="c3">0 / 300</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-divider"></div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label class="form-label"><span class="zh-only">联系方式（选填）</span><span class="en-only">Contact (optional)</span></label>
            <input class="form-input" type="text" name="联系方式" placeholder="邮箱、微信、LINE ID 均可" />
          </div>

          <button class="submit-btn" type="submit" id="submitBtn">
            <span id="btnText"><span class="zh-only">提交投稿</span><span class="en-only">Submit</span></span>
          </button>
          <p class="form-note zh-only">提交即表示您同意我们将信息用于网站内容更新</p>
          <p class="form-note en-only">By submitting you agree to your information being used for site updates</p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="success-card" id="successCard">
        <div class="success-icon">✓</div>
        <h3 class="zh-only">已收到，谢谢！</h3>
        <h3 class="en-only">Received, thank you!</h3>
        <p class="zh-only">我们会尽快核实并更新。<br>如果你留了联系方式，有疑问时我们会回复你。</p>
        <p class="en-only">We'll verify and update soon.<br>If you left contact info, we'll reach out if we have questions.</p>
        <div class="success-actions">
          <button class="success-btn success-btn-primary" onclick="resetForm()">
            <span class="zh-only">再提交一条</span>
            <span class="en-only">Submit another</span>
          </button>
          <a href="/" class="success-btn success-btn-secondary">
            <span class="zh-only">返回首页</span>
            <span class="en-only">Back to home</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <div>© {year} 81日本 · 由81Japan维护</div>
    <a href="/" style="color:var(--ink-3); text-decoration:none; font-size:12px;">
      <span class="zh-only">← 返回首页</span>
      <span class="en-only">← Home</span>
    </a>
  </footer>

  <script is:inline src="/submit.js" defer></script>
</Layout>
